response.overview: Suicidal Productions, a failing paranormal YouTube channel, meet to discuss new stories in a last ditch effort to save their channel. The story they pick...The Legend Of Carl Cobb! A drunk farmhand whose body was never found. How did he die? Is He haunting the fields? Nobody Knows for sure as the body count continues to rise. All we know is he's one mean Mothershucker!
response.tagline: Stay the shuck out of his fields!
response.title: Mothershucker
